text: The Székesfehérvár District () is a district in central-western part of Fejér County. Székesfehérvár is also the name of the district seat in the Székesfehérvár District. The Székesfehérvár District is located in Central Transdanubia. == Municipalities == The district has 1 urban county, 2 towns, 4 large villages and 18 villages.
